@page "/about"
<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-9">

            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <span class="badge rounded-pill text-bg-primary px-3 py-2">About</span>
                <h1 class="mt-3 fw-bold display-6">PDF IT Yourself</h1>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                    Powerful PDF tools that respect your privacy.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Mission -->
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm faq-card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>
                        PDF IT Yourself was created to provide powerful PDF manipulation tools that respect your privacy.
                        In an era where most online tools upload your files to remote servers,
                        we believe there’s a better way.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Why -->
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm faq-card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Why PDF IT Yourself?</h3>

                    <p>Traditional online PDF tools require you to upload your files to their servers. This raises concerns:</p>

                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> Sensitive documents exposed to third parties</li>
                        <li><strong>Security:</strong> Files could be stored or intercepted</li>
                        <li><strong>Speed:</strong> Upload & download delays</li>
                        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Requires internet & server availability</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Solution -->
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm faq-card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Our Solution</h3>

                    <p>
                        PDF IT Yourself processes everything locally in your browser using modern web technologies:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li><strong>WebAssembly:</strong> Near-native performance</li>
                        <li><strong>Web Workers:</strong> Parallel processing</li>
                        <li><strong>Modern JavaScript:</strong> Efficient file handling</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Open Source -->
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm faq-card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Open Source</h3>
                    <p>
                        PDF IT Yourself is open source and available on GitHub.
                        We believe in transparency and welcome contributions.
                    </p>

                    <a class="btn btn-dark mt-2"
                        target="_blank"
                        href="https://github.com/Ibrahim-Jallouli/PDF_IT_Yourself">
                        <i class="bi bi-github me-2"></i>View on GitHub
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>


            <!-- Support -->
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm faq-card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Support</h3>
                    <p>
                        PDF IT Yourself is free to use and always will be.
                        If you find it useful, consider:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="mb-3">
                        <li>⭐ Starring our GitHub repository</li>
                        <li>📢 Sharing it with others</li>
                        <li>🛠 Contributing or reporting issues</li>
                    </ul>

                    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark"
                        target="_blank"
                        href="https://github.com/Ibrahim-Jallouli/PDF_IT_Yourself">
                        <i class="bi bi-github me-2"></i>Get Involved
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

